{"tid":2289834,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有一位手足好需要大家嘅支持 代post","createTime":"2020-11-17T14:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T15:39:56.000Z","uid":6783,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7f88774fcf39a5d24800a697fbd85dfd34840f46","tid":2289834,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"有一位手足好需要大家嘅支持  我爆咗開唔到post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">上庭手足有嘢想同大家講</span></span><br />\n聽日就係裁決，雖然係水官負責，但係我亦都已經作咗最壞打算，放心我承受到，對比上到區院嘅手足嘅刑期，我呢啲唔算係啲咩。<br />\n我希望假如我真係入咗去，大家可以帶着我嘅意志，代我繼續行落去。<br />\n嚟到呢個月，尤其是呢幾日每日，我都諗返起上年呢個時間香港發生咗啲咩，呢一切真係好難捱，我更加試過12號夜晚聽返中大MV版嘅海闊天空聽到喊咗。上年經歷過腥風血雨，隨時要面對生命危險，但係我會覺得我係做緊有意義嘅事，我係為大家嘅夢想而付出，我係保衛緊香港嘅核心價值，所以我真係寧願返返去上年，都唔想好似而家咁樣咩都做唔到。<br />\n由踏上呢一條路開始，我就知道我唔會行返轉頭。唔好再相信一國兩制呢個謊言，中共根本就係騙子，同佢哋提出五大訴求佢哋根本唔會接受，因為咁樣等同我哋只係搏緊佢哋嘅同情求佢哋比我哋，但係雙普選係基本法一個莊嚴嘅承諾，佢哋憑乜嘢要香港人同佢哋談判。既然呢個大話已經揭穿左，佢哋都已經weh爛塊面，咁樣我哋根本冇可能再喺佢哋手上面爭取到啲咩。<br />\n要香港重光，用革命嘅方式獨立，真係唯一出路，但係我哋香港人呢個民族一定要自強，先至可以做到。所以我希望大家唔好放棄，我相信總有一日會喺街頭同大家再見。<br />\n民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n丸<br />\n17/11/2020 （1118裁決前夕）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#0925屯門 D2湯手足（18）被捕5次（93九龍灣42C巴士，925屯門，理大，38大埔管有非工，928煽惑縱火）曾還押64日。<br />\n<br />\n聽日裁決+判刑，佢講過送車想聽到大家唱天琦嘅 &lt;十八&gt;，講過近日唔開心想大家陪佢 <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iD8jTLBJ8vI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiD8jTLBJ8vI&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=fc013f89\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iD8jTLBJ8vI</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F18663&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a2d895bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18663</a><br />\nTg link為手足上庭時間表，由被捕人士關注組制作。其他內容並非出自關注組亦不代表其立場<br />\n另外以下為部分背景特殊手足，極需要大家支持<br />\n⭐️觀塘中午，李手足判四個月再提堂（大機會入返去還數）<br />\n⭐️觀塘上午，李手足係莫子聰仆街判‼️<br />\n⭐️粉嶺下午，非法集結判刑，係蘇文隆判‼️<br />\n⭐️屯門下午2手足裁決判刑，湯手足已認非法集結，有嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wongcon9/601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwongcon9%2F601&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=ee509230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wongcon9/601</a>"},{"pid":"150b19d8c83be0d9908d9eabbc238a7c623a6223","tid":2289834,"uid":368881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667cd8d66eba464c708d39222a18d9283b189621","tid":2289834,"uid":368881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"有時間希望大家可以去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9218a767b4ad0e3b75b0a8aeebc95ea86f3820","tid":2289834,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"150b19d8c83be0d9908d9eabbc238a7c623a6223","tid":2289834,"uid":368881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:06:43.000Z","msg":